    "The effectiveness of superpixel segmentation methods in image segmentation tasks was highlighted.",
    "• Datasets and their Impact: Various datasets such as ADE20K, Pascal VOC, and COCO were discussed, demonstrating the wide range of real-world problems that ML and DL technologies can address.",
    "The paper emphasised how dataset selection influences concept-based explanations and model performance.",
    "• Medical Applications of ML and DL: The review highlighted several applications, including early detection of diseases such as melanoma and image segmentation.",
    "It investigated deep learning for skin lesion classification, indicating a significant potential in medical imaging and diagnostics."
